  "recipeInstructions": "1. Preheat oven to 350 degrees F.\n2. Mix all ingredients together well.\n3. Place 1/3 cup (2 oz.) mixture in each of 16 muffin cups.\n4. Bake at 350F until done, about 1 hour. Remove from muffin tins.\n5. Serve hot or cold.",
